117
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:54,560
Down in one!

118
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,360
Girl, I haven't seen you before.

119
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,600
Hello.

120
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,120
