134
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,400
Come on, drink!

135
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:21,880
Cheers.

136
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:23,960
Nice to meet you.

137
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:24,440
Nice to meet you.

138
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,160
Welcome, Ms. You.

139
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:25,920
Cheers.

140
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,720
Isn't Shanshan amazing?

141
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:34,320
Truly amazing.

142
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,840
Then, I'll leave you to enjoy dinner.

143
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:36,800
Have a good time.

144
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:37,120
Okay.

145
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:37,720
Great.

146
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,800
Bye-bye.

147
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:39,360
See you.

148
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:39,880
Okay.

149
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:40,680
Bye.

150
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,320
Take care, Mr. Du.

151
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:42,320
Bye-bye.

