00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:43,800
Try the food.

153
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:44,760
Waiter.

154
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,480
Serve the hot dishes.

155
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:47,600
