156
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:50,400
These two beautiful girls are...

157
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:53,200
I had introduced them before you came.

158
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:54,320
This is my friend.

159
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:54,960
Bao Xue.

160
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:55,840
An actress.

161
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:56,480
This is her sister.

162
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,200
Xiaoyu.

163
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,159
Ms. Shanshan.

164
00:05:59,159 --> 00:06:01,640
Yu and Xue, meaning rain and snow.

165
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:02,800
Sounds chilling.

166
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:05,280
Then let's have a drink and get warm!

167
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:06,960
Great.

168
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,720
Shanshan, tell you what.

169
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:14,520
We'd already had a drink with Xiaoyu before you came.

170
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,520
From the moment she got here,

171
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,800
