174
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,840
Come on, Mr. Chai.

175
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:24,400
Her heart still needs a beat.

176
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:26,560
It needs to beat fast and strong.

177
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,360
Otherwise, we'd be drinking with a corpse.

178
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,520
You're right.

179
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:31,760
You are such a badass.

180
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:34,440
Here. I'll make a toast

181
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:36,600
to Ms. Shanshan, Mr. Chai, and Mr. Ge.

182
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:38,840
Sit down.

183
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,800
You can't toast to the three of us with just one drink

184
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,280
