185
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,760
Down in one!

186
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:48,920
Okay.

187
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:00,040
See?

188
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,000
Impressive.

189
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:01,920
Amazing, huh?

190
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,520
Yeah.

191
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:05,520
Are you born a great drinker

192
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:07,240
or did you practice to get this good?

193
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,840
I think it runs in the family.

194
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:13,360
My grandpa could drink a lot when he was alive.

195
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,680
He drank alcohol his whole life

196
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,040
without damaging his liver.

197
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,440
I think

198
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:20,440
he's got more ALDH in his body than others.

199
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:21,120
Do you need

200
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:23,920
one more shot of anesthetic than others in surgery?

201
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,920
One more is not enough.

202
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,680
I need general anesthesia even for a tooth removal.

203
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:29,960
See?

204
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:31,120
A group of

205
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:31,880
young people

206
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:33,800
with dreams and ambition.

207
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,680
The church looks good.

208
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,400
Right?

209
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:37,760
They think businessmen

210
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,159
are all under-educated.

211
00:07:40,159 --> 00:07:41,320
But let me tell you this.

212
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,640
Those who've made a fortune

213
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:46,120
can't be stupid.

214
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:48,240
What's that song again?

215
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:51,000
No one can become successful effortlessly.

216
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,840
You need to understand how important money is

217
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:55,080
so that you can save money.

218
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:56,000
Got it?

219
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:58,520
It doesn't matter if I got it.

220
00:07:58,520 --> 00:08:00,120
I don't have money to save.

221
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,360
Then make some.

222
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,680
How?

223
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:05,080
Here is an opportunity for you right now.

224
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,640
I'm all ears.

225
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:09,640
Have dinner with me.

226
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,080
Don't take me wrong.

227
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:20,360
A large part of our business

228
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:21,320
is publicity.

229
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:24,160
A lot of contracts are signed on the dinner table.

230
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,400
Xiaoyu,

231
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,160
you're good-looking.

232
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:28,920
You're elegant.

233
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:30,440
You're well-educated.

234
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:32,080
These are your advantages.

235
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,520
Use them!

236
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:37,240
I don't know your business well.

237
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,720
You can learn!

238
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:41,600
As long as you know a little bit, you're good to go.

239
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:42,919
Okay.

240
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,880
I'll think about it, alright?

241
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:45,840
Understood?

242
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,800
Think it over.

243
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:47,880
No pressure at all.

244
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:48,600
Okay.

245
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,960
Shanshan said you two are from the same city.

246
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:51,520
Yeah.

247
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:52,560
Where are you from?

248
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:53,880
Jingzhou, Hubei.

249
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:57,320
Jingzhou, as in the Jin Province Liu Bei lost?

250
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:57,960
Yeah?

251
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,880
Yeah.

252
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,480
How long have you been in Beijing?

253
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:03,360
My boyfriend came here for his Ph.D.

254
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,720
So, I came here with him.

255
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,560
Should be three years now.

256
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,480
Three years?

257
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:11,000
Then he's graduated now, right?

258
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,080
He got offered a fellowship.

259
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:14,320
God!

260
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:16,360
A mega intellect!

261
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,680
How did you meet?

262
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:20,880
We were classmates in middle school.

263
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:23,080
He had good grades

264
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:25,240
and got into a university in the provincial capital.

265
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:28,280
I started to work after graduating from
 the vocational school.

266
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:30,960
He went to grad school
 after obtaining his bachelor's degree.

267
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:34,360
I used to get on the long-distance bus
 and visit him every month.

268
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:37,880
Then he started his Ph.D program and went to Beijing.

269
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:40,000
I thought to myself,

270
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:42,040
"It's more than 1,000 km."

271
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:43,600
So, I quit my job

272
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,880
and came here to be with him.

273
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,960
Luckily, a relative of mine is abroad,

274
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,240
so I can live in his apartment.

275
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,720
It's right next to my boyfriend's uni.

276
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,720
Do you live together?

277
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:52,560
No.

278
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:55,560
